name: Scooby and the GAN, Part 3: The Spooky Swamp
description:
Scooby escaped The Haunted Forest by passing through a giant soap bubble wall that shimmered in the night. Now he finds himself in The Spooky Swamp and everywhere he looks, the tree stumps and animals are trying to change their forms to look more like him. Run, Scooby, run! Hopefully none of them will be able to follow you back to the rest of the gang.

Note: No input image was used for this VQGAN+CLIP art.

3200x2368 pixel PNG
